    <td colspan="3" class="bigNote" style="font-size: 13px; color: #222; background-color: #ffffff; border-color: #eee; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 1px 2px;" bgcolor="#ffffff">
	
	<a name="debt-shift" id="debt-shift" style="color: #0047d9;"></a><a class="headline" href="http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/credit-cards/balance-transfer-credit-cards?utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=bignote-two&amp;utm_term=02-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=credit-cards&amp;utm_content=1" style="color: #0047d9; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 20px; text-decoration: none;"><em class="urgent" style="color: #b31717; font-style: normal;">New.</em>  Longest-EVER 35 months 0      <span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #222; font-weight: bold;"> Slash the cost of existing credit card debts by &pound;100s or &pound;1,000s  by shifting them to interest-free for almost 3 years</span></a><br />
      Don't wait for January's bill to deal with credit card debts. Balance transfer NOW - which means you get a new card that pays off old card(s) for you, so you now owe it at a lower rate - to get yourself debt-free more quickly &amp; cheaply. 
      <ul>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 22px; margin-left: 0;"><strong>New top balance transfers. </strong>Accepted new <a href="http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/redir/c3cfeef6?utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=bignote-two&amp;utm_term=02-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=redir&amp;utm_content=2" target="_blank" style="color: #0047d9;">Barclaycard*</a> (<a href="http://www.msetool.co.uk/redirect/credit_cardeligibility?url=https://creditcards.moneysavingexpert.com/?bggow" target="new" style="color: #0047d9;">eligibility calc</a>) cardholders can now shift debt to it for a new record 35mth 0        </li>
      </ul>
