				<ul>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 22px; margin-left: 0;"><strong>The Balance Transfer Golden Rules. </strong>It's not just about picking the right card, it's about using it the right way...<strong><br /> </strong> <br />
				a) Don't just apply in hope, that marks your credit file. Instead use our <a href="http://www.msetool.co.uk/redirect/credit_cardeligibility?url=https://creditcards.moneysavingexpert.com/?balance-transfer" target="_blank" style="color: #0047d9;">Eligibility Calc</a> to find your best chance first. <br />
				b) Never miss the min monthly repayments, or the bank is  allowed to end your 0				c) Ensure you clear the card or  transfer  again before the 0				d) Don't spend/withdraw cash on these. It usually isn't at the   cheap rate &amp; cash withdrawals hit  your credit file.<br />
				e) Unsure what to pick? Use our <a href="http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/credit-cards/balance-transfer-credit-cards?utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=bignote-two&amp;utm_term=02-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=credit-cards&amp;utm_content=12#tool" style="color: #0047d9;">Which Card Is Cheapest?</a> tool. Full help in <a href="http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/credit-cards/balance-transfer-credit-cards?utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=bignote-two&amp;utm_term=02-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=credit-cards&amp;utm_content=13" style="color: #0047d9;">Best Balance Transfers</a> (<a href="http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/credit-cards/credit-card-apr-examples?utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=bignote-two&amp;utm_term=02-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=credit-cards&amp;utm_content=14" style="color: #0047d9;">APR Examples</a>).</li> </ul>
				
