     <td valign="top" colspan="2" class="mscBox pollbox" style="font-size: 13px; color: #222; background-color: #ffffff; border-color: #eee; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 1px 2px;" bgcolor="#ffffff"><h4 style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #d90057; border-bottom-style: solid; color: #000 !important; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 11px; text-shadow: 0 1px 0 #fff; font-size: 15px; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal;"><em>This week's poll: Did you go shopping-mad in the 'January sales'?</em></h4>
