      <td colspan="3" class="mscContent" style="font-size: 13px; color: #222; background-color: #ffffff; border-color: #eee; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 1px 2px;" bgcolor="#ffffff"><p class="funnybox" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 22px;"><strong>Do you know your its from your it's? </strong></p> <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 22px;"><em>That's it for this week, but before we go, how good are you at using apostrophes? Take this <a href="http://forums.moneysavingexpert.com/showthread.php?p=67292280&amp;utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=msccontent&amp;utm_term=02-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=forum&amp;utm_content=1#post67292280" style="color: #136c82;">quick quiz </a>to find out. </em></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 22px;"><em>We hope you save some money,</em></p>
     <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 22px;"><em>Martin &amp; the MSE team</em></p></td>

