                </strong>Founded in February 2003, it's now the UK's biggest consumer help website with over 9 million people getting this email and nearly 13m using the site. In September 2012 it became part of the MoneySupermarket Group PLC. Its focus is simple: how to save cash and fight for financial justice on anything and everything. The site has over 30 full time staff about half of whom are editorial researching, analysing and writing to continually find ways to save money.<em> More info</em>: See <a href="http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/site/about-the-site?utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=msetip&amp;utm_term=02-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=site&amp;utm_content=26" style="color: #0047d9;">About MSE</a></p>
